hivis.data

Class DataSeriesGeneric<V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • hivis.data.DataSetDefault
      • hivis.data.AbstractDataSeries<V>
        • hivis.data.DataSeriesGeneric<V>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataSeries<V>, DataSet, Iterable<V>

    public class DataSeriesGeneric<V>
extends AbstractDataSeries<V>
    Generic data series implementation. If the data is numeric then the specialised series classes, for example DataSeriesReal should be used for efficiency.
    Author:
    O. J. Coleman
